Things Needed for this to Run:
	Django 1.2+ (easy_install python-django)
	Nginx (apt-get install nginx)
	python-memcached (easy_install python-memcached)
	python-flup (easy_install python-flup)
	python imaging library (easy_install python-imaging)
	south (easy_install south)
	memcached (apt-get install memcached)
	django-stdimage (svn checkout http://django-stdimage.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/stdimage)
	postgresql_psycopg2 (apt-get install python-psycopg2)
    postgresql (apt-get install postgresql)
    tn3-gallery jQuery Plugin (Download)
    jQuery (Google AJAX CDN)

Things to add: 
    Ask Brad about photo sizes, gallery layout

Advantages:
    Self hosting
    DB Backing
    Ease of updates
    Templating
    Speed  
    Caching
